articles.title: US Fed Decision: S&P 500, Nasdaq hit new records with the street projecting more cuts - CNBC TV18 - CNBCTV18
articles.description: Gains were led by big tech with Tesla and Nvidia surging over 3.5% each. Oracle Corp., after a strong earnings performance, surged 13%. The 10-year treasury yield fell nine basis points to 4.32%.
